                  "revisionId": 2784034,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For a short time after Update 10.6 (2013-10-30), this mod could have been acquired via Transmutation . [1] This was due to a bug where all mods, including unreleased ones such as this one, became obtainable through transmutation. This has since been fixed, but players who obtained the mod this way were allowed to keep them. It was then made untradable so there was no other way to obtain this mod."
                }
